					<common:class level="1">Other waste</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Copper-based mixed waste is the main raw material, with other auxiliary materials, including coal, electric power, high-grade copper scrap, quartz sand, limestone, and lime. It generates intermediate products and waste slag, such as secondary slag, sponge copper, and anode copper mud residue. This waste has a hazardous component and a radioactive component, regulated under both the Resource Conservation and Recovery Act (RCRA) and the Atomic Energy Act. Copper waste can also be incinerated, converting it into new materials like heat, gas, steam, and ash.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">铜基混合废料是主要原料，其他辅助材料包括煤、电力、高级废铜、石英砂、石灰石和石灰。它会产生中间产品和废渣，如二次渣、海绵铜和阳极铜泥渣。这些废物具有危险成分和放射性成分，受《资源保护与回收法》（RCRA）和《原子能法》的监管。铜废料也可以进行焚烧，将其转化为热量、气体、蒸汽和灰烬等新材料。</common:generalComment>
